<section id="home" class="pt-28 pb-16 px-6 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="md:col-span-3 relative">
      <div class="tag mb-4 -rotate-1">ΕΔΩ ΨΗΝΟΥΜΕ ΑΠΟ ΤΗΝ ΚΑΡΔΙΑ</div>

      <h1 class="section-title mb-4">
        <span class="underline-paint">ΚΑΛΩΣ</span><br>
        <span class="text-orange">ΉΡΘΕΣ</span><br>
        ΣΤΟ "ΚΥΜΑ ΣΤΟ ΧΥΜΑ"
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-snug max-w-lg font-medium">
        Εκεί που η σούβλα περιστρέφεται με αγάπη και το φαγητό έχει γεύση <strong>παρέα, κάρβουνο και μεράκι</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#menu" class="btn-retro">ΔΕΣ ΤΟ ΜΕΝΟΥ</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-retro btn-retro-dark">ΚΡΑΤΗΣΗ</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-2 relative">
      <div class="relative -rotate-2">
        <div class="bg-cream border-[6px] border-ink shadow-block-lg p-4">
          <img src="/kymastoxyma_logo.jpg" alt="Κύμα στο Χύμα λογότυπο" class="w-full h-auto sepia-img block" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 z-20 bg-orange text-cream px-5 py-3 border-4 border-ink shadow-block font-display text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rotate-2">
        Από το 1960
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-16">
    <div class="bg-ink text-paper py-3 border-y-4 border-ink overflow-hidden">
      <div class="marquee-track">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-10 px-6 font-display text-xl uppercase whitespace-nowrap">
          <span>ΚΑΡΒΟΥΝΟ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΜΕΡΑΚΙ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΠΑΡΕΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΣΟΥΒΛΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΧΥΜΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΑΥΘΕΝΤΙΚΟ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-10 px-6 font-display text-xl uppercase whitespace-nowrap">
          <span>ΚΑΡΒΟΥΝΟ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΜΕΡΑΚΙ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΠΑΡΕΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΣΟΥΒΛΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΧΥΜΑ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
          <span>ΑΥΘΕΝΤΙΚΟ</span><span class="text-orange-bright">✦</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-12 px-6">
    <div class="meander-bar"></div>
  </div>
</section>
